            "html": "Sometimes a samsaran perishes under especially dramatic emotional circumstances, causing its soul to wander the Ethereal Plane before finally reincarnating. This spirit journey frays the samsaran\u2019s connection to his past lives but strengthens his ability to read others\u2019 pasts and present."
